Row: SunVic Chemical Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, is engaged in the manufacture and sale of intermediate chemical products primarily in the People’s Republic of China, rest of Asia, Europe, North America, and South America. It provides acrylic acid (AA) products, including purified AA and glacial AA; arylate esters comprising butyl acrylate, methyl acrylate, ethyl acrylate, and 2-ethylhexyl acrylate; N-phosphonomethyl lminodiacetic acid products; and glyphosate. The company’s products are fundamental chemicals used in the production of various industrial, consumer and agricultural products, such as coatings, adhesives, diapers, textiles, detergents, water treatment materials, and herbicides. It is also involved in the import and export of chemical products, as well as in the manufacture and sale of methyl tertiary-butyl ether and petroleum products. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Singapore. SunVic Chemical Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of DBS Vickers Securities (Singapore) Pte Ltd.
